; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the error path when balanced virtual postings don't balance and
; there is no null virtual posting to absorb the difference.

2024/01/01 Test unbalanced virtual
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash               $-50.00
    [Budget:Food]              $50.00
    [Budget:Savings]           $10.00

test bal -> 1
